Package com.example.fire_and_based

Class Event

java.lang.Object
com.example.fire_and_based.Event
All Implemented Interfaces:
android.os.Parcelable, Comparable<Event>
public class Event extends Object implements android.os.Parcelable, Comparable<Event>
Represents an event. This class implements Parcelable to allow event objects to be passed between activities.
